ğŸš€ Django Task Management API

A full-stack Django application built as a demo task for the Full Stack Data Engineer role.
This project demonstrates REST API development, database integration, and a simple data visualization dashboard.

ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This application allows users to:

Create, update, delete, and view tasks

Store data in PostgreSQL

View task analytics using a dashboard

Access REST APIs built with Django REST Framework

ğŸ›  Tech Stack

Backend: Django, Django REST Framework

Database: PostgreSQL

Frontend: HTML, Chart.js

Version Control: Git & GitHub

Python Version: 3.10

